<br>
OK....thats 2 words. No one ever said warriors are smart. <br>
<br>
However, without these two things, you will have no chance. You can try a druid/shaman sow..but a smart cast will negate that or even cast snare or similar spell. You will need sow potions cause if you lose sow your nuking opponent will get far enough away to start nuking you from Ohio. you can't beat a caster if you can't BEAT a caster. You dont't have spells so if he can keep you a safe distance from him he will never lose. The key is resisting his nukes with magic resist (gear or buffs will be fine) and always keep him in melee range. If he can't cast he can't win. If he waste all his mana on resists he can't win. <br>
<br>
