<br>
With my equipment on, my MR is near 150, which doesn't leave from FOR any spells.<br>
<br>
I've dueled clerics and one has gotten annull off on me.<br>
<br>
A class with damage shield can usually own me unless I have pumice.  I have jboots which help a lot =)<br>
<br>
Most casters it takes very little time to widdle down their health, and whenever I see &quot;soandso begins to cast a spell&quot;<br>
Zyce kicks YOU for 28 points of damage!<br>
You have been stunned!<br>
Very simple =)  There's really no way to snare a warrior either, so you can't kite them.<br>
<br>
I have a nice little baggy of resist gear, just throw on the appropriate gear for whatever class I'm dueling and I can resist about 95% of magic based spells, and 50-60% of anything else.  I can snare with a silken whip, soul bond you, boil blood you, can even tash you, and then break out the dual bloodpoints and lifetap the living hell out of you.  Throw on a fungi tunic and get the same regen as a lv 60 druid gets from their regen spells.  No, warriors aren't the best duelers, but you can be smart about dueling.<br>
<br>
<br>
